Package com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.util.transformers

Interface Summary
ITermTransformer Implementors of this interface represent objects which are capable of transforming the structure of Terms.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTermTransformer This class provides a lightweight framework for implementing Term parsers intended to transform Terms.
ConjunctionNormalFormTransformer This parser is used in order to put a Term into Conjunctive Normal Form.
NegationNormalFormTransformer This transformer brings a Term into Negation Normal Form.
NormalizeArithmeticComparatorsTransformer  
NormalizeArrayTermsTransformer Created by christopher on 08/01/14.
OrderOperandsTransformer Transformer which rebuilds a Term in such a way that all Junctors having the same operands, also have them in the same order.
RemoveAxiomaticExpressionsTransformer This transformer simplifies a Term by removing from it expressions which, in the context of Java, may be considered axiomatic.
RemoveDisjunctionsTransformer This transformer eliminates all disjunctions from a Term.
RemoveIfThenElseTransformer A Transformer which removes IfThenElse assertions from a Term, replacing them with a semantically equivalent conjunction of conditions.
RemoveImplicationsTransformer Instances of this transformer removes implications from terms.
RemoveObserverFunctionsTransformer  
RemoveSortDependingFunctionsTransformer  
SimplifyConjunctionTransformer  
SimplifyDisjunctionTransformer This Transformer simplifies the disjunctions present in a Term.
TermSimplificationTransformer Created by christopher on 20/01/14.
 

Exception Summary
TermTransformerException
